net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util

Class ComponentTreeIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util.ComponentTreeIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<Component>

    public class ComponentTreeIterator
extends Object
implements Iterator<Component>

    Provides an Iterator over a component tree. It is recommended that any code that needs to iterator over a component tree should use this class. Any changes in how component trees are handled will be reflected in this class and use of it can prevent future problems. The iteration is done using a breadth first ordering.

    If specific selection of components are required, this class may be subclassed and the canReturnComponent(Component) method overridden.

    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
